    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey friends! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my absolute dream car, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally babied, garage-kept, and looks absolutely stunning. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
