    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that defines showroom condition. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its deep, mirror-like finish and flawless body lines. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and every tactile surface feels as fresh as the day it left the factory. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, benefiting from a documented history of preventative maintenance and exclusive use of OEM parts. From the crisp response of the engine to the factory-tight suspension, this car delivers a peerless driving experience. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and a recent professional ceramic coating, this is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
