      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 997.1 Carrera S, featuring the 3.8L flat-six M97 powerplant. This specimen exhibits zero bore scoring and a dry undercarriage, indicative of meticulous thermal management and frequent lubricant analysis. The G97/01 6-speed manual transaxle offers crisp gate engagement with no synchro hesitation. Chassis dynamics are optimized by factory PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management), while the braking system retains its original bite via four-piston monoblock calipers. All factory tolerances are within spec, and paint meter readings confirm a factory-original finish across all panels. A true turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
